  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">A New Hope for Kibera&apos;s Orphans</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Kibera is Africa&apos;s largest urban settlement. Global One has schools in Kibera. We have operated successful, holistic programs since 2012 serving 1,500 children, women and men. Half the population consists of children under the age of 16. The majority lack the opportunity and finances to afford tuition. Childhood education is one of the strongest predictors of lifespan, longterm income, and health. It is a moral imperative.    Our Project Goal: a new modern school, equipped to serve 1500.</narrative>
  </description>
